{"id":9833,"date":"2024-02-26T11:16:37","date_gmt":"2024-02-26T11:16:37","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/klimacontra.com\/?page_id=9833"},"modified":"2024-05-30T06:43:26","modified_gmt":"2024-05-30T06:43:26","slug":"quality-policy-2","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/klimacontra.com\/quality-policy-2\/","title":{"rendered":"QUALITY POLICY"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\" wp-image-10323 alignleft\" src=\"https:\/\/klimacontra.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/qulaity2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"517\" height=\"322\" srcset=\"https:\/\/klimacontra.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/qulaity2.png 823w, https:\/\/klimacontra.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/qulaity2-600x374.png 600w, https:\/\/klimacontra.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/qulaity2-350x218.png 350w, https:\/\/klimacontra.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/qulaity2-150x93.png 150w, https:\/\/klimacontra.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/qulaity2-768x479.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 517px) 100vw, 517px\" \/>Klimacontra<\/strong>\u00a0will strive to provide products and services that meet or exceed the specifications and expectations of our customers. We are dedicated to continuously improve our products and services as measured by our customers. We will accomplish this through the excellence of our people and processes.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The company\u2019s business is focused on providing high quality of air movement products and HVAC accessories to meet the requirements and satisfaction of our clients. The intention is to be a coveted business partner and a reliable supplier.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The company aims to achieve the above by implementing a management system that complies with the internati